WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Jane sets up her easel overlooking the coastal bay.

00:02.500 --> 00:05.000
She carefully mixes warm orange and pink colors on her palette.

00:05.500 --> 00:08.000
With gentle brushstrokes, she captures the sunrise reflection on the water.

00:08.500 --> 00:12.000
"The key is to work quickly before the light changes," Jane explains.

00:12.500 --> 00:15.000
She adds delicate highlights to create the golden hour magic.